Tavatron thought for a moment:

"Yes, that sounds right. I heard rumors back on Cybertron, but nothing 
definite." Tavatron scrolled up on the comp screen, reading some of the 
information.

"It says here that he has recently joined our ranks." Tavatron turned back 
to Dinobot, the beads in her fur clicked against each other. Her stomach 
growled, it had been mega-cycles since her last meal.

"This could be useful."
